title: About Me
text:
I am a fourth year student at the University Of Toronto studying computer science, mathematics, and statistics. I am a coding enthusiast and I love to learn about new technologies. I have worked with UnisolTech for four years where I developed and maintained technologies in python, java, and C. I have also been working with the RCMP for the past year as a technical analyst.
